/**
 * Multiple Quill instances can be configured with the same toolbar DOM
 * container (`modules.toolbar.container`). All the `Toolbar` module
 * instances bound to that container share this bookkeeping so that
 * clicking/changing a control acts on whichever editor most recently had
 * a selection or focus ("the active editor"), and so that DOM controls,
